{STAR EVOLUTION} Put on one of your RexStars or Nature creatures. (When this creature would leave, the top card leaves instead.)
{TRIPLE BREAKER}
■ When you put this creature, put the top card of your deck into your mana zone. Then you may choose an evolution creature from your mana zone that costs the same as or less than the number of cards in your mana zone and put that creature.
